.TH "lpfc_sli4_request_firmware_update" 9 "lpfc_sli4_request_firmware_update" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
lpfc_sli4_request_firmware_update \- Request linux generic firmware upgrade
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" lpfc_sli4_request_firmware_update
.BI "(struct lpfc_hba *phba "  ","
.BI "uint8_t fw_upgrade "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "phba" 12
pointer to lpfc hba data structure.
.IP "fw_upgrade" 12
which firmware to update.
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
This routine is called to perform Linux generic firmware upgrade on device
that supports such feature.
